<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="P" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Pictured" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Pictured,</orth> painted, represented: <cit><quote>where your true image p. lies,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 24.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 24, 6</bibl></cit>. <emph>I have not seen him</emph> (death) <emph>so p.</emph> (with eyes) <bibl n="shak. cym 5.4.185" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 4, 185</bibl>.
